#

Beef Wellington with Red Wine Reduction

$75
1200 kcal
Difficulty: 85%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-Free Option AvailableHigh ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

GourmetFine DiningSpecial OccasionLuxury

Description

A luxurious Beef Wellington enveloped in flaky pastry, paired with a rich red wine reduction and creamy chive mashed potatoes, complemented by sweet honey-glazed baby carrots and crispy Brussels sprouts.

Ingredients

  • Beef tenderloin: 2 lbs
  • Puff pastry: 1 sheet
  • Mushrooms (finely chopped): 8 oz
  • Prosciutto: 6 slices
  • Dijon mustard: 2 tbsp
  • Egg yolk: 1
  • Red wine: 1 cup
  • Beef stock: 1 cup
  • Heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • Chives (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • Potatoes (Yukon Gold): 2 lbs
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Honey: 2 tbsp
  • Baby carrots: 1 lb
  • Brussels sprouts: 1 lb
  • Olive oil: 3 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
